overview: Syed, Farhah, Armand and Kat lived happily ever after. Syed plans to introduce Farhah to other family members during the first day of Aidilfitri. Armand and Syed plan to have their wives cook their own meal at Armand and Kat's wedding reception. Farhah is not sure how to do it and is busy taking care of her baby while Kat is not good at cooking.
title: Tersuka Tanpa Sengaja Raya
